Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.74,0:01:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一天劍心聽說在左之助\N帶他去過的那家賭館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.84,0:01:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助的幾個朋友\N因吸食過多鴉片而死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.34,0:01:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後劍心救了被青年企業家\N武田觀柳手下追捕的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.75,0:01:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個謎樣女性。。。高荷惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.72,0:01:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另外武田觀柳的得力助手\N隱密天才四之森蒼率領的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.76,0:02:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,御庭番眾高手為奪回\N高荷惠偷襲了神谷道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.96,0:02:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心與左之助打倒御庭番眾\N高手火男與惡見的同時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.94,0:02:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥手腕卻中了毒螺旋鏢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.38,0:02:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到惠姑娘迅速\N為禰彥處理我們都太感驚奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.05,0:02:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助撿到了惠姑娘的藥\N卻對惠姑娘心存懷疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.09,0:02:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第九話\N最強的耐力軍團\N恐怖的御庭番眾高手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.60,0:02:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.57,0:02:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,熏姑娘！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.04,0:02:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥他。。。禰彥他。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.84,0:02:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐。。。難道。。該不會。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.38,0:02:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玄齊醫生！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.09,0:03:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經無大礙了\N好好休息一天就能完全康復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.89,0:03:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐你真壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.53,0:03:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嚇得我壽命縮短十年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.10,0:03:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來熏姑娘是喜極而泣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.74,0:03:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然嘍！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.27,0:03:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥的命總算保住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.37,0:03:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能得救真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.98,0:03:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玄齊醫生，真謝謝您！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.48,0:03:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您真不愧是東京第一名醫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.98,0:03:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要謝就謝寫這藥方的人好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.29,0:03:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可真不容易，從解毒藥材\N到調配方法寫得很完整
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.19,0:03:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不單純是醫學上的心得\N一定是位擅長藥劑的能人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.23,0:03:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人真是不可貌相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.43,0:03:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到惠姑娘是藥劑專家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.47,0:03:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惠姑娘如果真叫高荷惠的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.27,0:03:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高荷這姓。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.54,0:03:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對惠姑娘可真要刮目相看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.27,0:04:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連火男與惡見都被打敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.10,0:04:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人決非等閒之輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.14,0:04:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確，從他使太刀的手勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.34,0:04:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看得出功力深厚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.28,0:04:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，去調查這名劍客的來路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.88,0:04:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並隨時向我報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.68,0:04:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵命，我馬上辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.25,0:04:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紅髮左臉有十字疤\N那人該不會是。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.53,0:04:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知幾年沒做過胡枝餅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.44,0:04:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇！胡枝餅耶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.21,0:04:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小雀最愛吃胡枝餅了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.24,0:05:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小熏，左之助呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.91,0:05:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不在這裏，可能回到家後\N就一直在睡覺吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.08,0:05:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之也整夜看護禰彥，累了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.59,0:05:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時就看得出他很累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.66,0:05:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們先開始慶祝禰彥康復吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.59,0:05:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就不客氣嘍！哇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.06,0:05:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.03,0:05:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗚哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.00,0:05:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真好吃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.43,0:05:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好吃喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.44,0:05:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥你身體還沒完全好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.04,0:05:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以吃太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.87,0:05:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼話，小熏\N我一定要把我的份吃掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.55,0:05:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼！咽到了吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.21,0:05:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那。。那個惠姑娘\N能不能教我做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.35,0:05:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊！這很簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.19,0:05:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！那下次我來做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.22,0:05:53.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦！小熏做的能吃嗎\N我寧願吃土也不你做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.77,0:05:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的，病是好了\N那張嘴還是一樣壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.97,0:06:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被我說中了吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.00,0:06:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！禰彥的臉都是胡枝餅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.77,0:06:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥成了胡枝餅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.15,0:06:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們感情真好，好像一家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.98,0:06:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別說笑了，有這種丑姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.99,0:06:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是太倒霉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.76,0:06:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才要說像你這種弟弟\N送我都不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.56,0:06:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起來真像親姐弟在吵架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.98,0:06:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是，惠姑娘你家人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.08,0:06:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.95,0:06:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.22,0:06:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去幫你們泡茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.99,0:06:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是不是問了不該問的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.06,0:07:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家真的都是好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.63,0:07:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對這些好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.33,0:07:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這東西你要怎麼解釋？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.20,0:07:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何你身上有這種東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.71,0:07:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是鴉片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.72,0:07:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鴉片？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.65,0:07:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看你還有什麼話說？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.99,0:07:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做出這種東西的人。。。是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.46,0:07:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來就是你害宵太他們\N害死我朋友的就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.80,0:07:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢著，左之助\N惠姑娘告訴我你的苦衷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.00,0:07:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼你要做鴉片？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.04,0:07:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惠姑娘該不會是\N高荷隆生的女兒吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.91,0:07:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！你怎麼知道\N我父親的名字？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.99,0:07:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏。。。輪到小雀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.99,0:08:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這步可難下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.23,0:08:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然不出所料，會津高荷家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.16,0:08:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是代代出名的家族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.07,0:08:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因捲入會津諸侯間挑起的\N會津戰爭，隆生戰死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.71,0:08:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母親與哥哥因戰亂行蹤不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.78,0:08:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當時高荷家還有一位幼女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.95,0:08:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那名幼女就是惠姑娘嘍！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.29,0:08:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時一定受了很多苦吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.22,0:08:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當時受的苦比起後來\N實在算不了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.10,0:08:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,五年前我從會津上京城來\N寄宿在一位醫生家當助手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.27,0:08:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.34,0:08:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻和觀柳合夥做鴉片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.38,0:09:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後來那位醫生被殺\N換成我來做鴉片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.32,0:09:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,觀柳。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.75,0:09:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直努力要成為\N象父親那樣優秀的醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.19,0:09:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到最後卻成了\N作藥害死人的兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.70,0:09:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好幾次都想死卻下不了決心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.77,0:09:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以惠姑娘才逃離觀柳掌握
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.64,0:09:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他想大量開發害人的鴉片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.91,0:09:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣會害了很多人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.08,0:09:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我才逃跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.72,0:09:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而知道如何製造鴉片的\N只有小惠小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.39,0:09:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以觀柳才會急著抓你回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.93,0:09:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,觀柳真的不是好東西\N不可原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.83,0:09:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們會不擇手段的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.17,0:09:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還是暫時待在這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.60,0:09:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.44,0:10:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要再責備自己了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.48,0:10:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小惠小姐\N還有很長的路要走。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.82,0:10:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不對，熏小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.22,0:10:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對呀我也瞭解一個人的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.36,0:10:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果玄齊醫生及劍心也死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.80,0:10:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也會和你一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.64,0:10:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.27,0:10:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我無法和她在同一屋檐下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.08,0:10:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因她害死了宵太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.91,0:10:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在左之助\N還無法整理自己的情緒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.82,0:10:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後一定會諒解的，惠姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.37,0:11:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惠姐姐.跟我們一起玩啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.84,0:11:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惠姐姐跟小雀玩啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.01,0:11:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，等我把衣服洗完
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.11,0:11:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我們等你喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.54,0:11:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思打擾你了\N請問有沒有要幫忙的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.85,0:11:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒。。。沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.95,0:11:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧！既然你沒什麼要幫忙\N那我這邊可有要你幫忙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.76,0:11:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武田觀柳正在等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.17,0:12:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,御庭番高手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.58,0:12:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.48,0:12:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像我字條寫的\N我決不會傷害惠姑娘你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.65,0:12:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只希望你能乖乖回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.86,0:12:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我回去再幫你做鴉片嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.96,0:12:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然！那不是你的工作嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.26,0:12:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你還不懂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.84,0:12:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我為何沒尋死是因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.57,0:12:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活著學醫說不定哪一天\N還可見到失散的家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.35,0:12:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼希望著才一直沒尋死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.98,0:12:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了別再說了\N惠姑娘你一定會見到你家人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.99,0:13:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過我已經下定決心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.89,0:13:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,見不到家人也無所謂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.66,0:13:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果要我再做那害人的藥\N那我寧願一死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.20,0:13:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就只有你死不得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.94,0:13:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果神谷道場無故失火\N孩子的屍體橫陳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.01,0:13:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認為怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.41,0:13:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.05,0:13:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣警戒都沒有用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.75,0:13:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對御庭番眾高手來說\N縱幾場火易如反掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.36,0:13:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.10,0:13:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你從我這裏逃走太大意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.00,0:13:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算想死也死不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.00,0:13:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你應該不希望\N再有人因為你而死吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.28,0:13:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們倆已是焦不離仲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.78,0:14:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒不如繼續好好配合下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.32,0:14:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論過去和未來都一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.55,0:14:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我等你嘍！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.09,0:14:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了！今晚要特別小心火災
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.66,0:14:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼不現在就帶走高荷惠？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.83,0:14:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連武田觀柳碰到斬人拔刀齊\N都要忌他三分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.10,0:14:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果高荷惠自己想要走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.24,0:14:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊有多厲害都一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.61,0:14:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這和殺人無關\N我想他也無用武之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.52,0:14:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用武之地。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.89,0:14:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首領，有隻老鼠潛入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.92,0:14:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管他，除了斬人拔刀齊\N緋村劍心外其他人不足掛心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.96,0:14:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.54,0:15:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃不開了，觀柳或鴉片\N一輩子都逃不開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.02,0:15:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惠姑娘該你洗了\N惠姑娘？我進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.40,0:15:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心！惠姑娘她。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.17,0:15:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？留書？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.84,0:15:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惠姑娘說她要回會津去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.04,0:15:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.88,0:15:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼一聲招呼不打就走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.45,0:15:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都還沒好好向她道謝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.22,0:15:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪，即使回去會津。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.39,0:15:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,家裏也沒有人等惠姑娘回去\N糟了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.77,0:16:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？要回觀柳那裏去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.64,0:16:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請放心，我答應過你\N不會再做害死你朋友的鴉片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.42,0:16:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那觀柳會就諒解嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.05,0:16:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說到做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.16,0:16:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你讓開我有急事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.16,0:16:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛那麼急著死呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.13,0:16:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有熏小姐、劍心和我\N你就不要再擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.20,0:16:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的意思是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.24,0:16:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快回去吧！\N小姐他們都在道場等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.27,0:16:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再說你家人也不知道在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.58,0:16:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經無所謂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.21,0:16:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使找到我也沒臉見他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.79,0:16:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是做鴉片的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.32,0:16:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的過去是無法輕易抹煞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.96,0:16:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要以為自己多可憐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.60,0:17:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,背負著無法抹煞過去的\N又不是只有你一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.84,0:17:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算你死了也救不回我朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.51,0:17:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活著倒還能贖罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.04,0:17:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再說你總有一天能見到家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.58,0:17:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死了誰都見不到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.95,0:17:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.22,0:17:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喔！躲得過我一擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.83,0:17:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來你倒是有幾分功夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.73,0:17:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡！是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.77,0:17:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,江戶城御庭番高手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.80,0:17:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,城中護衛長式尉就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.31,0:17:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不乖乖把那女的交出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.68,0:17:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就叫你粉身碎骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.77,0:18:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用這種小道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.30,0:18:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就不會打啦？三腳貓！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.47,0:18:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我堂堂城中護衛長\N竟敢叫我三腳貓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.91,0:18:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敢看輕我式尉要你後悔一輩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.08,0:18:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧！小毛頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.09,0:18:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有骨氣，我出招了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.23,0:18:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不痛不癢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.27,0:18:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.33,0:18:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就讓你見識見識\N御庭番手式尉的力氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.15,0:18:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真。。。真是驚人的力道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.13,0:19:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.19,0:19:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,省省力氣吧！\N能傷我頭蓋骨就很了不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.87,0:19:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要傷我腦袋\N憑你的能耐是不太可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.71,0:19:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,御庭番高手之一的我\N全身鍛煉得像盔甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.58,0:19:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,碰到擁有無敵力氣的我\N算是你倒霉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.82,0:19:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算我同情你，讓你一點吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.77,0:19:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能還有這麼大力氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.00,0:20:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,稱得上最強或無敵的\N這世上只有劍心一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.04,0:20:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武田觀柳手下烏合之眾\N組成的御庭番眾自稱無敵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.58,0:20:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豈不笑死人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.75,0:20:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這混蛋，你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.26,0:20:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頭再怎硬\N腦子還是一樣不堪一擊吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.71,0:20:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.88,0:20:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！混蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.32,0:20:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高荷惠我帶走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.09,0:20:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.12,0:20:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助，你還好吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.06,0:20:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先別管我，那女的。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.93,0:20:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惠姑娘！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.77,0:20:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙受到觀柳威脅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.33,0:21:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了保護小姐你們\N決定回到觀柳身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.77,0:21:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然不出我所料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.71,0:21:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是拼了命也要去救她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.28,0:21:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是救不回她\N怎稱得上活人劍神谷活心派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.78,0:21:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥。。沒錯！\N我們說到做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.68,0:21:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥。。熏小姐。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.92,0:21:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.89,0:21:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！左之！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.86,0:21:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是左之助！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.16,0:21:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,越挫越勇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.46,0:21:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那。。。我們走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.99,0:21:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.64,0:23:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了要救惠姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.41,0:23:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們潛入了觀柳宅邸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.71,0:23:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那裏碰上了隱密天才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.01,0:23:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四乃森蒼紫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.78,0:23:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心與蒼紫隨即展開激戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.85,0:23:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下集的浪客劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.72,0:23:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫，俊美過人的恐怖人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.52,0:23:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敬請期待

